videoSnippet.title: 11-year-old Aditya Mittal Crushes a Grandmaster with a Blistering Attack
videoSnippet.description:

His tiny figure barely reaches the table, but, sitting in his rather big wheel chair, he appears intimidating.

Aditya Mittal  vs.  Niaz Murshed
Event: 10th KIIT International Category - A, 2017.05.29, Queen Knight Variation, QGD (D31)

1. d4 d5 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. Nf3 Nf6 5. cxd5 exd5 6. Bg5 Nbd7 7. e3 c5 8. Be2 Qa5 9. O-O Bxc3 10. bxc3 Ne4 11. c4 Nc3 12. Qc2 Nxe2+ 13. Qxe2 dxc4 14. Qxc4 cxd4 15. Qxd4 O-O 16. Rac1 Nb6 17.
